yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？海盗说的话让人有点难以理解。

yingyinNormal.en: We are sailing to Pirate Island. Goodbye Grampy Rabbit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要驶向海盗岛了。再见，兔爷爷。

yingyinNormal.en: Happy birthday, Danny. It's been the best pirate party ever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 祝你生日快乐，丹尼！这个是最好玩的海盗生日派对了！

yingyinNormal.en: Danny Dog likes being a pirate. Everyone likes being a pirate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼小狗喜欢当海盗。大家都喜欢当海盗。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny's Pirate Party
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼的海盗派对

yingyinNormal.en: George, you could wear my pirate hat. Today, we are sailing to pirate island.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，你可以带上我的海盗帽。我们今天要开着船，到海盗岛去。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy? Can you read the pirate's message? Hmm. This pirate has very bad handwriting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，你能帮我读一下海盗写的纸条吗？这个海盗的字写得真难看.

yingyinNormal.en: Why is he talking funny? That's pirate's talk. If you want to play my pirate game, say Arrr. Arrr.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么说些奇怪的话？他说的是是海盗用语。想玩我的海盗游戏的孩子们，请说，啊。啊。

yingyinNormal.en: The pirate's handwriting is excellent. No, I can't make it out at all. The pirate has clearly written, "Follow the arrows." Follow the arrows?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得海盗的字写得挺不错的。可是我一个字都看不懂。海盗写得很清楚啊，跟着箭头走。跟着箭头走？

yingyinNormal.en: Good bye, Pirate Island. See you again soon. I love Pirate Island. Can we visit it again? Of course we can, Peppa. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再见了，海盗岛。我们很快会再见的。我很当然可以了 佩奇喜欢海盗岛。我们以后能再来玩吗？当然可以了，佩奇。太好了！

yingyinNormal.en: Have you had a lovely time? We went to pirate island. And to a lighthouse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们玩的开心吗。我们去了海盗岛玩。我们还去了灯塔。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny Dog has a dressing-up box full of pirate clothes. Ah, my hearties.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼小狗有一个服装箱子，里面全部是海盗的衣服。啊，我的心肝儿。

yingyinNormal.en: I can see something glittering. It's a coin. Maybe it's a pirate's treasure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我能看到一些闪闪的东西。是枚硬币。有可能是海盗留下的宝藏啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Well done, Peppa. Let's see what the message says. Oh, it's a message from a pirate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做得好，佩琪。来看看这条上写了什么，这个是海盗送来的纸条。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny Dog is playing in his pirate den. Here are Peppa and her friends. Hello, Danny. Hello everyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼小狗在他的海盗小屋里玩。佩奇和她的朋友来了。你好，丹尼。大家好。

yingyinNormal.en: Grandpa Pig and Polly Parrot are gardening the pirate treasure. What does that mean? Run to the boat. Yo hoho.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爷爷和鹦鹉波利守护着海盗宝藏。这是什么意思？跑到船上去吧。哟吼。

yingyinNormal.en: Today is Danny Dog's Birthday. He is having a party. Yoo hoho. Everyone has come dressed as a pirate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是小狗丹尼的生日。他要举办一个生日派对。哟吼吼！大家都打扮成了海盗的样子。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone is excited to be playing a pirate game. Hello, Grandpa Pig. We are on our way. Jolly good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人都很兴奋的想要玩这个海盗游戏。你好，猪爷爷，我们要出发了。非常好。非常好。

yingyinNormal.en: If we are lucky, we might find buried treasure. Pirate Island sounds like a great place. Land, ahoy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果幸运的话，我们还能找到被埋藏的宝藏。海盗岛听起来像是个不错的地方。看到陆地啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Who have we here? I'm a pirate. Shiver me timbers. I'm a witch. I can turn you into a frog. I'm a clown.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是谁呀？我是一个海盗，这下你害怕了吧？我是一个巫婆，我能把你变成青蛙。我是小丑。
